<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
  <div>
    <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Master → Kelas</div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Import Masal Kelas</h1>
    <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600">Upload Excel (.xlsx) / CSV untuk menambah atau memperbarui data kelas berdasarkan <b>kode</b>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex gap-2">
    <a href="/admin/classes" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100">Kembali</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 p-5">
    <div class="text-lg font-semibold">Langkah & Format</div>
    <ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
      <li>Download template CSV, lalu isi data kelas (boleh juga Excel).</li>
      <li>Kolom wajib: <span class="font-mono text-slate-900">code</span>/<span class="font-mono text-slate-900">kode</span>, <span class="font-mono text-slate-900">name</span>/<span class="font-mono text-slate-900">nama</span>.</li>
      <li>Jika <b>code</b> sudah ada, sistem akan <b>update</b> nama kelas.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <a href="/public/templates/class_import_template.csv" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 text-sm">Download Template CSV</a>
      <a href="/public/templates/class_import_template.xlsx" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 text-sm">Download Template XLSX</a>
    </div>

    <details class="mt-4">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm text-slate-600">Contoh isi template (klik untuk lihat)</summary>
      <pre class="mt-3 text-xs whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200 p-4 text-slate-600">code,name
X-RPL-1,X RPL 1
XII-TKJ-2,XII TKJ 2
</pre>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 p-5">
    <div class="text-lg font-semibold">Upload Import</div>
    <form action="/admin/classes/import/preview" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="mt-4 space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="text-sm text-slate-600">File Excel/CSV</label>
        <input type="file" name="file" accept=".xlsx,.csv,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet,text/csv" required class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3" />
      </div>
      <button class="w-full rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 text-white font-semibold py-3">Preview & Validasi</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
